text: Access could be hindered by the construction work going on in the vicinity, but the reception of the friendly staff shall make up for it.
Superb customer service.  Reliable fleet of vehicles with a wide range of variety.  Reasonable rental rates across the board.  Two thumbs up!

When I return the vehicle I'm sure they take all the gas out and so the next person will have to fill up more gas than they need as well.

DO NOT RENT FROM THEM!!
